-[Sandy sighs]
-What?

15:27.845 --> 15:28.685
[quietly] I'm sorry.

15:28.765 --> 15:30.205
What? What's the matter?

15:32.245 --> 15:33.085
You're sad.

15:33.845 --> 15:34.925
