It was brilliant.

15:39.485 --> 15:41.285
Now it's over. It's not your problem.

15:42.405 --> 15:43.965
-Did you not want any kids?
-No.

15:44.965 --> 15:48.445
-Annoying little fuckers.
-[laughs and sighs]

15:49.365 --> 15:50.245
[inhales sharply]

15:50.325 --> 15:51.965
