15:52.045 --> 15:53.525
[whispering] I'll try, but stop crying

15:53.605 --> 15:55.565
because people will think
I said something awful.

15:55.645 --> 15:57.485
-Okay.
-[whispering] Okay. Shhhh.

15:58.245 --> 16:01.605
See, this is why I don't want kids.
They're too snotty and pathetic.

16:01.685 --> 16:02.925
[Sandy laughs]

16:03.485 --> 16:04.485
Oh!

16:04.565 --> 16:05.965
I think he's gonna eat. Watch this.

16:27.445 --> 16:29.885
-He told you to watch me eat, didn't he?
-Yeah.

16:30.525 --> 16:32.205
-Thoughts?
-It's fine.

16:33.285 --> 16:35.485
No, exactly. I put the food in my gob,

16:35.565 --> 16:37.725
I chew it, I swallow it,
just like everyone else.

16:37.805 --> 16:40.725
But from here,
it looks like that super photography

16:40.805 --> 16:45.805
when they sort of magnify a snail,
like one thousand times, eating a cabbage.

16:45.885 --> 16:48.765
No, nothing like that.
You'd never catch me eating cabbages.

16:48.845 --> 16:50.765
My granddad never used to eat cabbages.

16:50.845 --> 16:53.325
Did he die of diabetes like he's gonna?

16:53.405 --> 16:54.485
No, bowel cancer.

16:57.125 --> 16:58.805
Do you get <i>any</i> fiber in your diet?

16:58.885 --> 16:59.845
Yeah, loads.

16:59.925 --> 17:02.045
-What fruit and veg?
-Meant to have five a day.

17:02.165 --> 17:03.885
How many portions do you have a day?

17:03.965 --> 17:05.285
-Ten.
-Potatoes don't count.

17:05.365 --> 17:06.485
None, then.

17:23.645 --> 17:25.725
-[air horn hoots]
-[Lisa screams]

17:25.805 --> 17:28.765
-[Tony laughing hysterically]
<i>-Oh, my God, Tony!</i> [laughs]

17:29.725 --> 17:32.565
-<i>You're such a dick!</i>
-[Tony laughing] <i>Oh!</i>

17:32.925 --> 17:34.285
<i>-That's really good.</i>
-[Lisa] <i>Thanks.</i>

