-[Braden] Hey. You all right?
-Good. All right, George?

17:50.205 --> 17:53.165
-So I'll be back about seven.
-Make sure it's seven. I've got a thing.

17:53.245 --> 17:55.165
-Okay, no worries. See you then.
-Yep.

17:55.525 --> 17:56.965
Be a good boy for Uncle Tony, George!

17:58.685 --> 18:02.245
Um, maybe don't bring up
the wanting to kill yourself thing.

18:03.445 --> 18:04.325
As if I would.

18:04.845 --> 18:06.725
Sorry. Yeah, I know. Okay.

18:08.005 --> 18:09.205
What if he brings it up?

18:10.565 --> 18:11.645
Why would he bring it up?

18:12.725 --> 18:13.565
He wouldn't.

18:14.045 --> 18:15.005
It was a joke.

18:15.085 --> 18:16.125
Oh. [laughs feebly]

18:17.485 --> 18:19.165
-All right, see ya later.
-See ya later.

