18:48.765 --> 18:49.605
Yep.

18:50.125 --> 18:51.085
I'm sad too.

18:51.805 --> 18:53.805
I dream about her sometimes.

18:55.125 --> 18:56.165
Me too.

18:56.245 --> 18:58.205
Why didn't the doctors make her better?

19:00.165 --> 19:01.005
